&lt;p&gt;Hi there! We are Testlio, a global software testing company with its own freelance network. Our freelancers test apps from companies across the globe. Testlio is a great place for people who value the freedom and flexibility of remote work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the moment, we are looking for freelance software testers based in Poland who own Magenta TV Subscriptions (with set-top-box), working on T-Mobile internet connection (broadband). If you have such a setup, we&#39;d like to invite you to participate in our client&#39;s project, where we&#39;ll be testing their app to ensure the highest possible quality. Your work will help them improve their services for users such as yourself, as well as others throughout Poland.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To participate in this project, you will need to create an account on our platform. Through this account, we can assign you testing tasks. You will be asked to use our website for defect tracking and will receive materials to prepare you for testing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Benefits of being a freelancer at Testlio&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule: You can create your schedule and work on other testing runs that interest you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: Testlio is a 100% remote company. Seriously, you can work from the coffee shop, your home, or while waiting for class.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Growth: You’ll be testing global-scale mobile apps and have the chance to boost your skills and grow your career.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment: You are paid by the hour, not by the bug. This means you get paid even if you did not uncover any bugs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Age: You have to be at least 18 years old.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: Must be physically located in Poland..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability: This is a freelance project, meaning that working hours are limited. At the moment, we&#39;ll be running this project throughout the month of June. We will assign tasks every week, sometimes several times per week.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devices: Magenta TV STB (set-top-box) working on a T-Mobile internet connection.&amp;nbsp;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We&#39;re also looking for someone who, in addition to the STB, has an iOS device. This is not a mandatory requirement, but nice to have.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: Software testing experience is a plus, but if you are new to testing, we offer free courses to help you learn and grow.&amp;nbsp;We offer a preparatory course that will help you learn more about testing on our website.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What does testing look like?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type of testing: functional, streaming testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type of work: short-term, freelance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Workload: Each testing task can last&lt;strong&gt; 2 to 4 hours&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pay rate: The hourly pay rate for this is 15 USD/hr.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus payrates are also available:&amp;nbsp;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$50 USD for participating in at least 1 test run.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$25 USD for referring a friend who has the setup we are looking for!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment: You are paid weekly via PayPal or Payoneer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We will send you the USD amount, which you can then transfer/convert to EUR if it is more convenient to you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;How to start?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fill out the application below to start. From there, our team will get in touch with instructions about the next steps, which will include information on how to create a Testlio account and how to access the project.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions or need help, please contact Opportunities@testlio.com using the code MAGENTA PL in the Subject line/email body so we can quickly identify your request&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
