&lt;p&gt;Hi there! We are Testlio, a global software testing company with its own freelance network. Our freelancers test apps from companies across the globe. Testlio is a great place for people who value the freedom and flexibility of remote work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the moment, we are looking for freelance software testers based in &lt;strong&gt;Louisiana &lt;/strong&gt;to join us in testing a popular wagering app.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have partnered with a wagering app who regularly updates their product every two weeks. This happens around&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3:00 AM – 5 AM US local time&lt;/strong&gt;, during low-traffic periods, which is why we are looking for testers who would be available during this time to perform smoke testing on iOS mobile, Android Mobile and Web.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;paragraph has-block-align-none&quot;&gt;Here are some examples of the tasks you’ll be asked to perform:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;wp-block-list list list--unordered nitro-offscreen&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list__item&quot;&gt;Providing concise notes and evidence (screenshots / screen recordings if requested in the run).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list__item&quot;&gt;Launching the product on your available platform(s).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list__item&quot;&gt;Creating a consumer account on a wagering platform, which will include going through a KYC (know-your-customer) flow. Because this platform complies with US federal and state regulations, you will be required to use your own legal information to register. You should be prepared to provide: Full Legal Name and Date of Birth; Current US Address; Social Security Number (SSN)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list__item&quot;&gt;Running through key wagering flows (for example: placing a wager, checking wager status, basic navigation, and other core actions defined in the run instructions).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;list__item&quot;&gt;Capturing and reporting any functional issues, crashes, obvious UI defects, or blocking problems in the wagering flow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Benefits of being a freelancer at Testlio&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule: You can create your schedule and work on other testing runs that interest you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: Testlio is a 100% remote company. Seriously, you can work from the coffee shop, your home, or while waiting for class.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Growth: You’ll be testing global-scale mobile apps and have the chance to boost your skills and grow your career.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment: You are paid by the hour, not by the bug. This means you get paid even if you did not uncover any bugs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Age: You have to be at least 21 years old.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Location: Must be physically located in &lt;strong&gt;Louisiana&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability: You have to be available to test between 3:00 AM - 5:00 AM US local time for 30 to 1h.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Devices: You will need an Android Phone or Tablet in order to participate in this project.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience: Software testing experience is a plus, but if you are new to testing, we offer free courses to help you learn and grow.&amp;nbsp;We offer a preparatory course that will help you learn more about testing on our website.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What does testing look like?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type of testing: smoke testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type of work: short-term, freelance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Workload: Approximately 30 minutes to 1h of work every few weeks when the client&#39;s app receives an update.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pay rate: The pay rate for this is $30 USD/hr.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment: You are paid weekly via PayPal or Payoneer.&lt;/li&gt;
