&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You get real autonomy:&lt;/strong&gt; No micromanagement here. You get to figure out how to take our product knowledge and tool workflows and translate them into a language that actually makes sense to a quota-carrying seller in their day-to-day life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll have a voice with leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; This isn’t a role where you hide in the background. You’ll be talking directly with senior leadership, showing them the metrics of how our teams are progressing, and directly influencing how we go to market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
